- if @vacancy.errors.any?
  .error-summary{role: 'alert', tabindex: '-1'}
    %h2.heading-medium.error-summary-heading
      = pluralize(@vacancy.errors.count, 'error')
      prevented this vacancy from being saved:
    %ul
      - @vacancy.errors.full_messages.each do |message|
        %li= message

